cription><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ypurtx7.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/iukUmES</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Cyberball2073]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Hours of daylight as a function of latitude and and time visually represented.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/b1Rb0x4</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0kFbv9q.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Interesting way to see the solstice happen. Wanted to share this cool infographic, so here it is.

 Have a good weekend.

As a 'TLDR' post script: the prime meridian is the 'up and down' line in the middle of the picture. 

Before '72 and atomic clocks, this line was used as the standard for calibrating international time zones.

Here it serves as a 'control baseline' to show changes in daylight as a result of the Earth's tilt and its orbit around the sun.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/b1Rb0x4</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[embeddedinrealityviaQED]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A moderately sized DK dump of stolen memes for these trying times 725.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/giUTZim</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VSbv6lA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XCbR5Ii.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Nglxwdm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DqDj4FD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/x4XcnE6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vapme5X.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sAUjozO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jntOOnA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bf92nqB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ota78CU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gaD8Slu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5YvCrjy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"